## Performance Metrics

Expected processing time:
- Simple PDFs (1-10 pages): 2-5 seconds per PDF
- Complex PDFs (50+ pages): 10-30 seconds per PDF
- CrossRef lookup: 1 second per DOI (with rate limiting)
- Database insertion: 1-2 seconds per paper + relations

Total for 100 PDFs: ~30-45 minutes (with rate limiting)

## Data Privacy

- PDFs are stored in Supabase `papers.full_text` column
- Use RLS policies to restrict access
- CrossRef API lookups are anonymized
- No data sent to OpenAI without explicit enablement
