## Output

### Database
Papers inserted into Supabase tables:
- `papers` - Full metadata + text
- `compounds` - Extracted compounds
- `pathogens` - Extracted pathogens
- `paper_compounds` - Relationships

### Wiki Markdown
Created in `docs/science-wiki/ingested-papers/`:
